welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Overlea, the charming city known for its quaint streets, friendly locals, and rich history. We invite you to embrace the city's charm and explore all that it has to offer. Enjoy your stay in Overlea!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at BWI handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is primarily used by Southwest Airlines for their domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B is used by various airlines for their domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C is used by various airlines for their domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse D
terminals.description: Concourse D is primarily used by Delta Airlines for their domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse E
terminals.description: Concourse E is primarily used by international airlines for their flights to and from BWI.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tipton AAF Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at Tipton AAF Airport is used exclusively for military flights and operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lee Airport handles all commercial flights and includes a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Lee Airport caters to private and charter flights, with upscale services and facilities available.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network throughout the terminals.
